snippet.title: Just the Two of Us are Harder, Better, Faster, Stronger than You (3x SU mashup)
snippet.description:
Steven Universe x Daft Punk x Grover Washington Jr
DOWNLOAD https://mega.nz/#!G1tDTBLK!jfpGlKDstfjxnLdL3x7U5z2tCAfTRzuzAwR5T3xQHPM
INSTRUMENTAL https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4Emjqa4BBwA
TUMBLR POST http://scibot9000.tumblr.com/post/115696971328/just-the-two-of-us-are-harder-better-faster
SOUNDCLOUD https://soundcloud.com/sci_/jt2ouahbfsty
I'm not going to sell this particular mashup, but if you still feel like throwing money my way, do peruse my discography on bandcamp: https://soundsfromsci.bandcamp.com/

-----

I made a mashup on a whim one day, posted it to tumblr, and it got a ton of notes even though it wasn't that great. 
So I redid it. :P

song list:
1. Daft Punk - Touch
2. Daft Punk - Harder, Better, Faster, Stronger
3. Grover Washington Jr - Just the Two of Us
4. Steven Universe (surrashu, aivi, estelle, jeff lui, jeff ball, rebecca sugar) - Stronger than You
5. a very large number of random breaks, and also a very brief chord from Jimi Tenor - Paint the Stars

many thanks to rikuta for the art!
http://rikuta.tumblr.com/

do you want to use this in your video/podcast/whatever? as long as you're not selling it or claiming that you made the mashup, feel free to use it wherever you want!
